CREATE TABLE "Articles_21" (
    "Id" TEXT NOT NULL CONSTRAINT "PK_Articles_21" PRIMARY KEY,
    "CreatedTime" TEXT NOT NULL,
    "CreatedBy" TEXT NULL,
    "Rank" REAL NOT NULL,
    "Status" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    "CreatedTimeTicks" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    "Title" TEXT NOT NULL,
    "Descr" TEXT NULL,
    "CategoryId" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT "FK_Articles_21_Categories_CategoryId" FOREIGN KEY ("CategoryId") REFERENCES "Categories" ("Id") ON DELETE CASCADE
);
